The '''Portugal women's national football team''' represents [[Portugal]] in international [[Women's association football|women's football]].  The team, controlled by the [[Portuguese Football Federation]] (FPF), play in [[2011 FIFA Women's World Cup qualification - UEFA Group 7|UEFA Group 7]] of [[2011 FIFA Women's World Cup]] qualifying, ending in August 2010.

